research/history/round_summaries/round_0068.json:36:      "r67 对 `lowrank_expert_topk NUM_EXPERTS=64` 的负结果更像是在否定“trunk+更大 routed capacity”的继续扩容，而不是完全否定 routed-only MoE-like 方向。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0068.json:37:      "本轮是对 `expert_topk` true sparse-capacity mode 的继续验证：保持 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1` 与 `K=192` 不变，只放大总静态 expert 容量。"
research/history/round_summaries/round_0068.json:40:      "如果 `NUM_EXPERTS=32` 明显优于 r51，则下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `K=160` 或 `128`，测试这条 routed-only 前沿能否进一步向左延伸。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0068.json:41:      "如果 `NUM_EXPERTS=32` 改善很弱或再次出现明显吞吐回退，则可较清晰判定纯 routed sublibrary 扩容在当前 target 上已接近饱和，后续预算应更多回到 `lowrank_expert_residual` 或其他带 residual cleanup 的结构。",
