research/history/round_summaries/round_0150.json:20:    "hypothesis": "最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(h(x))} α_i^sh(h(x)) b_i^sh + Σ_{e∈E(h(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e(h(x))} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j} + Σ_{m∈S_res(x-x_stage1)} γ_m(x) c_m，其中 h(x)=ReLU(Bx) 是共享低秩投影，{b_i^sh} 是 shared 静态库，{b_{e,j}} 是 routed expert 静态子库，{c_m} 是全局 residual 静态补偿库，x_stage1 是 shared+routed factorized stage 的重构。导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 推理链路时仍是“shared library lookup + routed expert sublibrary lookup + residual lookup + 有限加权和”，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此该 family 判定为扩展兼容；`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 等不兼容 family 仍不能驱动 frontier。唯一主假设：在保持 r146 的 matched recipe（K=112、EF=1、FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256、NUM_EXPERTS=64、ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2、LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=224、STAGE1_RATIO=0.25 与其余训练配方不变）的前提下，新加 `shared_routed_factorized_expert_residual` 能回答当前最缺的结构问题：把 hetero MoE 的 shared+routed factorized head 再接上 residual cleanup，是否能在约 0.47x total_cost 下形成比现有 `<0.5x` anchor 更有价值的新结构段。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0150.json:41:      "本地 allowlist 校验通过：`validate_env_overrides` 现在接受 `ARCHITECTURE=shared_routed_factorized_expert_residual` 搭配 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM`、`NUM_EXPERTS`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT`、`STAGE1_RATIO`。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0150.json:42:      "按架构接线 checklist 做了 exact smoke：`ARCHITECTURE=shared_routed_factorized_expert_residual, K=112, EF=1, FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256, NUM_EXPERTS=64, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=224, STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` 可 instantiate、forward、backward。",
